nodes.text: Darth Tagros was a Sith Lord of the reconstituted Sith Empire during the Galactic War.
Darth Tagros was intended to appear in Patch 2.0.0 of Star Wars: The Old Republic, but was ultimately cut. The character exists within the game files with a placeholder model.
